title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data in a table inside a grid cell
OB: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from a table that is nested inside a grid cell.
EB: When exporting data from two tables, the expected result is that the data is successfully exported. However, the actual result is that an exception occurs in the 'ReportEngineService.getMetaData()' function.
SR: To reproduce this issue, follow these steps: 1) Insert a grid onto the page, 2) Insert a table inside one of the grid cells, 3) Attempt to export the data from the table.
